=== Purchase Information === Product Title: SXC Cosmetics Nail Polish Set, 15ml/0.5oz Full Size Nail Lacquer Gift lot (Pink, Metallic, Neon, Pastel, Gold & Glitter) (12 Color Set, Metallic Gold) Review Date: 2018/11/08 Store: SXC Average Rating: 4.2 Product Details: {'Brand': 'SXC', 'Item Form': 'Liquid', 'Finish Type': 'Shimmery', 'Age Range (Description)': 'Adult', 'Unit Count': '12 Count', 'Liquid Volume': '0.5 Fluid Ounces', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '6 x 4.5 x 3.75 inches; 1.75 Pounds', 'UPC': '738964869615'} Review Text: I was very happy to see these came in a pretty little giftable box and had cardboard separators as to avoid breakage. Also, the gold & bronze shades are perfect for fall. Review Title: Great colors Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Bamboo Charcoal Konjac Sponge Facial Cleansing Review Date: 2019/08/08 Store: Bamboo Product Description: ['For All Natural Facial Cleansing, For All Skin Types'] Average Rating: 3.6 Product Details: {'Material': 'Konjac', 'Brand': 'Bamboo', 'Style': 'Puff', 'Item Form': 'Loofah', 'Number of Pieces': '1', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '6.93 x 4.88 x 0.87 inches; 1 Ounces', 'UPC': '769898063213', 'Manufacturer': 'Bamboo'} Review Text: Not sure about this product. This is my 8th konjac sponge. I try different brands. This one is the thinnest one I've ever had, being about 1/3 of the thickness of others I have used. The thinness makes it feel very flimsy, so hopefully it will last as long as it should. Review Title: Thin sponge Rating: 3.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: VANALIA Gel Nail Polish Remover Kit - 2pcs of Gel Polish Remover & 1pc of Liquid Latex Tape Peel Off Cuticle Guard Skin Barrier Protector, 3-5 Minutes Easily & Quickly & Healthy Method, 45 ml Review Date: 2022/08/05 Store: VANALIA Average Rating: 3.6 Product Details: {'Package Dimensions': '4.9 x 4.1 x 1.3 inches; 7.2 Ounces', 'UPC': '717666053690'} Review Text: This review is for the VANALIA Gel Nail Polish Remover Kit. It comes with 2 bottes of of gel polish remover(doesn't smell bad), 1 bottle of liquid latex peel off cuticle protector, 1 cuticle pusher, 1 nail file, and 2 cleaning pads. First use the file to remove the top coat from your nails, brush the latex onto the skin around your nails, apply a thick layer or gel remover and wait 6 min, then use the pusher to remove polish, and then peel off the latex. Everything needed to remove gel polished nails is included. It all comes in a cute box. I think this would make a great gift when given along with a box of gel polishes. Review Title: Everything needed to remove gel polish. Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: essence | Welcome to London Eyeshadow Palette | 12 Highly Pigmented, Matte & Metallic Blendable Shades | Vegan & Cruelty Free | Free From Oil, Fragrance, Parabens, Alcohol, & Microplastic Particles Review Date: 2022/08/23 Store: essence cosmetics Average Rating: 4.0 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Essence cosmetics', 'Item Form': 'Powder', 'Finish Type': 'Metallic, Matte', 'Special Feature': 'Cruelty Free', 'Number of Items': '1', 'Product Dimensions': '6.73 x 2.52 x 0.47 inches; 0.46 Ounces', 'Item model number': '934871', 'Manufacturer': 'Cosnova'} Review Text: This review is for an essence Welcome to London Eyeshadow Palette. You get 12 eyeshadows in both matte and metallic shades. The eyeshadows blend well. I especially like the shimmery golden shade. There is a mirror inside, but no applicator. The case has a magnetic closure and is nicely decorated with a London theme. I think this would make a great gift. Review Title: Pretty palette. Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Stride Foot Cream Smoothes Rough Cracked Heels & Dry Skin –– Dematologist-Developed, Intensely Moisturizing Foot Cream with Aloe Vera, Coconut oil and Green tea Review Date: 2022/08/28 Store: Stride Average Rating: 4.0 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Stride', 'Scent': 'Coconut', 'Active Ingredients': 'Coconut oil,green tea,vitamin e', 'Unit Count': '4.0 Ounce', 'Number of Items': '1', 'Package Dimensions': '3 x 3 x 2 inches; 3.99 Ounces', 'UPC': '860006643317'} Review Text: This review is for a jar of STRIDE Foot Cream. This cream helps with rough heels and moisturizes dry feet.

The ACTIVE ingredients listed on the product page are:
Deionized water, green tea leaf extract, cocos nucifera (coconut) oil, dodecane, cetearyl alcohol, polysorbate 60.

The cream while in the jar has a soft, almost wipped appearance. When applying it feels kind of waxy, which feels soothing on my feet. The smell kind if a fresh scent and isn't very strong. I like this foot cream a lot. Review Title: Soothing foot cream. Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: LOKNGXU Eyebrow Pencil to Modify Eyebrows Easy to Color Waterproof Long-Lasting Non-Dizzy Makeup with Spiral Eyebrow Brush (4# Grey Brown) Review Date: 2022/09/24 Store: LOKNGXU Average Rating: 5.0 Product Details: {'Brand': 'LOKNGXU', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Product Benefits': 'Softening,Long Lasting', 'Package Information': 'Tube', 'Unit Count': '1.00 Count', 'UPC': '797442555327'} Review Text: This review is for a LOKNGXU Eyebrow Pencil (4# Grey Brown). I like that this brow pencil has an angled tip. The color lasted on by brows all day(I did use a setting spray). I will continue to use this product. Review Title: Color lasted Rating: 5.0 --------------------------------------------------

The purchase history reveals a clear preference for cosmetics and skincare products, particularly those that offer a variety of finishes (shimmery, matte) and colors. A consistent rating pattern highlights a strong satisfaction with quality and aesthetics, showing higher ratings for products that are visually appealing and well-packaged. 

Common themes emerge around gifting, as multiple purchases include elements suitable for presents, suggesting a preference for not only personal use but also for thoughtful gifting. Engagement with diverse beauty needs—nail care, facial cleansing, and eye makeup—indicates versatility in product use cases.

When it comes to quality, the individual shows a strong inclination toward cruelty-free and natural ingredients, as evidenced by the positive reception of products with vegan certifications. Price sensitivity appears moderate; while there is appreciation for affordable and functional items, the buyer favors products that deliver quality and effective results even at higher price points, opting for items with established brands.

Overall, the person's core preferences center on high-quality, visually appealing cosmetics and skincare solutions that are functional, versatile, and suitable for gifting, with a notable inclination towards cruelty-free and natural options.

target_interaction.title: Cute little device
target_interaction.text:
This review is for a MEIQIER Eye Massager with Natural Quartz Jade. I ordered this to replace a similar device that didn't have a Quartz head or blue light(just red). This device has a Rose Quartz tip, heat, massage, red light(collagen production) and blue light(calms inflammation) therapy. It uses USB charging. The eye massager comes with a protective tip cap/cover and looks like a cute lipstick.
I like to use first the red light, heat, massage with my eye serum and then I use blue light, heat massage, with my eyecream. I am using this device only on my eyes(I have full face device with a larger head). It feels very soothing on my eyes and helps with puffiness too. Since it is small and has a cap, it is easy to just toss it in a purse on the go. This device would make a great gift!
target_interaction.title_meta: MEIQIER Eye Massager with Natural Quartz Jade, Facial Massage Tool with Heat & Vibration for Eliminate Eye Bags, Dark Circle Remover Eye Lip Fine Lines, Promote Essence Absorption
